      • relabelsTo

        boolean relabelsTo(Label l,
                   java.util.Set<jif.lang.PrincipalUtil.DelegationPair> s)
        Returns true iff this <= l. If the method returns true, then s has all of the delegations (i.e., DelegationPairs) added to it that the result depends upon. If the method returns false, then s has no elements added to it.
